{"tid":913152,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我討厭冬天","createTime":"2018-11-23T07:42:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T09:24:20.000Z","uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0d2ff3d57ca247076794eddc9243a37cebea7a1a","tid":913152,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:42:52.000Z","msg":"我討厭冬天<br />\n<br />\n冬天是屬於有錢人的季節<br />\n<br />\n在這個季節，他們炫耀從國外買來的各種亮麗的大衣<br />\n<br />\n而我身上卻還是那件十年前從回收站撿到的二手衣服<br />\n<br />\n我特別討厭冬天"},{"pid":"ac5741ed93df8129ae0f97229989240690e1c2ec","tid":913152,"uid":38194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:45:14.000Z","msg":"夏天你都係着二手衫㗎啦，有乜分別"},{"pid":"d6e4b6b6183619eefff1ea03b9a0a6454717920b","tid":913152,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac5741ed93df8129ae0f97229989240690e1c2ec","tid":913152,"uid":38194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:45:14.000Z","msg":"夏天你都係着二手衫㗎啦，有乜分別"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:16:27.000Z","msg":"冬天會使我更自卑<br />\n<br />\n華麗的大衣充滿了我的視線，我並不能逃避他"},{"pid":"cf72889f49bde00dfabd87df344e7d78257066dd","tid":913152,"uid":18241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:46:33.000Z","msg":"有病就及早求醫"},{"pid":"dbb6e98387c582684be37346404db309d385c24f","tid":913152,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf72889f49bde00dfabd87df344e7d78257066dd","tid":913152,"uid":18241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:46:33.000Z","msg":"有病就及早求醫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T09:24:20.000Z","msg":"你是有錢人<br />\n<br />\n你過著豐衣足食的生活<br />\n<br />\n我和你不同"}]}